events.text: What? I thought there was an Elf Master! And Princess was enchanted
Enchantments? What did you think? I was kidnapped?
Well breaking news Mr. Hero! Life is not all about you. I came here myself. The goblines have hearts too! And I became their goblin queen.
But I thought I was your true love.
Who said I even liked you? You are one puny creature, everything you got is through nepotism. My children here buit everything by themselves. And now look what have you done.
Looks like I have some emmergency business with the neighbouring kingdom. Goodluck hero.
